Leads Management System

1. Tech Stack
- Frontend: Next.js
- Backend: Node.js
- Hosting: Vercel
- Version Control: GitHub

2. Data Model
- Profiles: id (PK), name, email (CK), companyId, password, gender, address, phone (CK), role, createdTime, lastEditedTime, isDeleted
- Companies: id (PK), name, email (CK), phone, address, note, createdTime, lastEditedTime, isDeleted
- Leads: id (PK), ownerUserId, assignedUserId, companyId, leadName, phone (CK), email (CK), status, location, note, createdTime, lastEditedTime, isDeleted
- Comments: id (PK), leadId, companyId, commentText, createdByUserId, status, createdTime, lastEditedTime, isDeleted

3. Roles & Permissions
- SuperAdmin: Full CRUD on users, admins, companies; Get/Edit/Delete leads & comments.
- Admin: CRUD on users, leads, comments within own company; View all admins in company.
- User: Create/Edit leads in company; Delete own leads; View all company comments; Add/Edit/Delete own comments.

4. Business Rules
- Immutable: id, leadId, commentId, companyId, ownerUserId
- Cascade Deletes: Lead → its comments; Company → all users, leads, comments
- Soft Delete: isDeleted = true
- Retention: Auto-purge after 30 days if isDeleted = true
- Lists: Search (phone/email), pagination, sort/filter

5. UI Structure
- SuperAdmin
  Sidebar: Companies, Leads, Comments, Admins, Users
  Dashboard: Create Company, Admin, User
- Admin
  Sidebar: Leads, Comments, Admins, Users, My Leads, My Work
  Dashboard: Create Lead, User
- User
  Sidebar: Leads, My Leads, My Work
  Dashboard: Create Lead

6. Pages & Actions
- View Company: Details + admins, users, leads; Edit/Delete
- View Admin: Details + comments; Edit/Delete (SuperAdmin only)
- View Lead: Details + comments; Add comment, Edit; Delete (SuperAdmin/Admin/Owner)
- View User: Details + comments; Edit/Delete
- View Comment: Details; Edit/Delete (SuperAdmin/Admin/Owner)
- Add Comment: leadId (fixed), status (dropdown, updates lead status), commentText
- Edit Company: name, email, phone, address, note
- Edit Admin: name, email, phone, password, gender, address
- Edit Lead: leadName, assignedUserId, email, phone, status, location, note
- Edit User: name, password, gender, address
- Edit Comment: text, status

7. Forms
- Create Company: name, email, phone, address, note
- Create Admin: name, email, companyId (dropdown), password, gender, address, phone
- Create User: name, email, password, gender, address, phone
- Create Lead: leadName, assignedUserId (dropdown of company admins/users), phone, email, status (default = New), location, note